<h2 id="vaki"><a href="#vaki" style="text-decoration: none">#</a> Vaki</h2>
<p>
  Vaki Aquaculture Systems Ltd. is the industry leader in fish counting and
  size estimation of live fish. Worked on the
  <a href="https://vakiiceland.is/biomass-daily/">Biomass Daily</a> system. A
  company operating salmon farms would rent hardware frames from Vaki and place
  them in the sea cages. As the salmon swim through the frames their weight is
  measured. This data is then aggregated and analysed in various dashboards.
  <a href="https://vakiiceland.is/">vakiiceland.is</a>
</p>
